title: The Watchmen booked to play The Burt
text:
Hometown rockers The Watchmen are returning to Winnipeg in the spring for a show at The Burt. 

The Watchmen — consisting of vocalist Danny Greaves, guitarist Joey Serlin, Ken Tizzard on bass, and Sammy Kohn on the drums — will play the Burton Cummings Theatre on March 24. 
Tickets starts at $32.50, plus fees and taxes, and are available through Ticketmaster starting Friday at 10 a.m. Sponsored Links The Watchmen booked to play The Burt
